defaultThe Government’s objective is to get investment levels back up to those in continental competitor economies, with capital spending on roads effectively ring fenced as 
defaultalr
defaulteady 
defaultis rail investment. There is little additional information in Action for Roads about the actual investment programme though there is a useful summary map on page 31 showing major projects starting by 2015, pipeline projects starting after 2015 and pin
defaultch point schemes. Several of these should be of direct benefit to ports. 
defaultPorts have been participating actively in Highways Agency workshops on route based strategies designed to identify bottlenecks and develop solutions.
